description: 600 80TH MOTORISED BRIGADE (ARCTIC) troops have conducted live firing exercises in extreme cold temperatures. The troops practicied firing small arms, RPG-7, and engaging targets while being towed behind A1 snowmobiles.
OPERATIONAL GROUP OF RUSSIAN FORCES IN TRANSNISTRIA troops have conducted counter-terror and security drills in TRANSNISTRIA. An estimated thirty troops took part in the exercises.
group_label: Operational Group of Russian Forces in Transnistria

description: CENTRAL MILITARY DISTRICT special purpose troops have conducted a training exercise in the ORENBURG REGION. The troops practiced marching deep behind enemy lines (upto 200 km) and attacking enemy camps while supported by Tigr armoured cars.
